    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "if",
      "zh": "如果",
      "ja": "もし",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm lost!",
      "zh": "我迷路了！",
      "ja": "迷子になった！",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where's the water?",
      "zh": "水在哪裡？",
      "ja": "水はどこ？",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just really...",
      "zh": "真的只是...",
      "ja": "本当にただ...",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dude, what do I talk?",
      "zh": "老兄，我該說什麼？",
      "ja": "ねえ、何を話せばいい？",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hell, will we stuck here forever?",
      "zh": "該死，我們會永遠被困在這裡嗎？",
      "ja": "くそ、ここにずっと閉じ込められるの？",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic.",
      "zh": "不要慌張。",
      "ja": "慌てないで。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic.",
      "zh": "不要慌張。",
      "ja": "慌てないで。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are trained for professionals.",
      "zh": "我們是受過專業訓練的。",
      "ja": "私たちはプロとして訓練されている。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now stay calm.",
      "zh": "現在保持冷靜。",
      "ja": "今は落ち着いて。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are going around the leaf.",
      "zh": "我們要繞過葉子。",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周りを回る。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Around the leaf?",
      "zh": "繞過葉子？",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周り？",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't think we can do that.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們做不到。",
      "ja": "それはできないと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, nonsense.",
      "zh": "哦，胡說。",
      "ja": "ああ、ナンセンスだ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is nothing compared to the tweak of 93.",
      "zh": "這跟93年的調整比起來算不了什麼。",
      "ja": "これは93年の調整に比べたら何でもない。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣。",
      "ja": "それだ。",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいぞ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're doing great.",
      "zh": "你做得很好。",
      "ja": "よくやっている。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There you go.",
      "zh": "就這樣。",
      "ja": "そうだ。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hell, you go.",
      "zh": "該死，你去吧。",
      "ja": "くそ、行け。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Watch my eyes.",
      "zh": "看著我的眼睛。",
      "ja": "私の目を見て。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't look away.",
      "zh": "不要移開視線。",
      "ja": "目をそらさないで。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And here's the line again.",
      "zh": "線又來了。",
      "ja": "そしてまた線が見える。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mr. Sorrell.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，索雷爾先生。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、ソレルさん。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good job, everybody.",
      "zh": "大家做得好。",
      "ja": "みんなよくやった。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my.",
      "zh": "哦，我的天。",
      "ja": "ああ、まあ。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's quite a gap, Mr. Sorrell.",
      "zh": "索雷爾先生，有很大的間隙。",
      "ja": "かなり隙間があるね、ソレルさん。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shouldn't we tell the queen?",
      "zh": "我們不應該告訴女王嗎？",
      "ja": "女王に知らせるべきじゃない？",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think we need to involve the queen in this.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們不需要讓女王介入這件事。",
      "ja": "これに女王を巻き込む必要はないと思う。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's got enough on her plate already.",
      "zh": "她已經有很多事情要處理了。",
      "ja": "彼女はもう十分忙しい。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Trading her daughter.",
      "zh": "交易她的女兒。",
      "ja": "彼女の娘を取引している。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "zh": "哦，是的。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだ。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Princess Adam.",
      "zh": "亞當公主。",
      "ja": "アダム姫。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The poor D.",
      "zh": "可憐的D。",
      "ja": "かわいそうなD。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    }
  ]
